headline: Retail inflation: Apparel, footwear prices see declines in April
summary: The April Consumer Price Index (CPI) data showed monthly and annual inflation rates dip below economists' forecasts. Yahoo Finance retail reporter Brooke DiPalma checks out several data points from the inflation print, noting price declines from major apparel companies and footwear brands. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here.
